paragraphs.text:
%spark
import org.apache.spark.mllib.linalg.Vectors
import org.apache.spark.mllib.clustering.KMeans
import org.apache.spark.sql.functions._

// load file and remove header
val data = sc.textFile("data/spykmeans.csv")
val header = data.first
val rows = data.filter(l => l != header)

// comma separator split
val allSplit = rows.map(line => line.split(","))

// map parts to case class
val allDataCC1RDD = allSplit.map( p => CC1( p(0).toString, p(1).toString, p(2).trim.toDouble, p(3).trim.toDouble, p(4).trim.toDouble, p(5).trim.toDouble, p(6).trim.toDouble, p(7).trim.toDouble, p(8).trim.toDouble, p(9).trim.toDouble))
allDataCC1RDD.cache()
allDataCC1RDD.saveToGrid()

val vectors = allDataCC1RDD.map(cc1 => Vectors.dense(cc1.rsi2, cc1.rsiClost3, cc1.percentageRank100, cc1.rsiStreak2, cc1.crsi))
vectors.cache()
